author: Kuokka77
description:
"Lupus Reditus" demo soundtrack by AceMan, demo ranked 1st at Revision 2025 Amiga demo compo.
Art from the demo by Vasyl (assuming, based on style)

Made using real A1200 Rev. 1D.4 audio.

Demo can be watched here (again real A1200 rec from sLASH):
https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=wJX8rApC4H8

Visit my channel for more Amiga music.
title: Amiga music: AceMan - Lupus Reditus demo OST (A1200🎧Dolbyfied)
